source: cli/tests/help.rs
expression: text
---
Completely remove the v1 or v2 free space cache

Usage: clear-space-cache <VERSION> <DEVICE>

Arguments:
  <VERSION>
          Free space cache version to remove
          
          [possible values: v1, v2]

  <DEVICE>
          Path to the btrfs device

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help
